Interface Summary
RoadType define road type, current only normal and highway are defined.

DigitalMap DigitalMap is the base class for VectorMap and RasterMap.
MapBrush Map brush used to paint a map region object.
MapCollection Class MapCollection stands for a collection of map objects.
MapDirection This class is used to store driving directions results
MapDirectionCommandElement Driving diretion command element.A direction for a MapStep consists at most 5 direction command elements and has following syntax [Command]-[Adj]-[Road Name]-[Adj]-[Road Name].
MapDirectionCommandType Driving diretion types.
MapLayer MapLayer defines a map layer.Computer maps are organized into layers.
MapLayerContainer MapLayerContainer is a collection of map layers.

MapNoneObject Class MapNoneObject stands for a map object without geo info.
MapObject Base class of all map objects.
MapPen Map pen set the pen properties to draw a map object.
MapPline Class MapPline stands for a map pline object.
MapPoint Class MapPoint stands for a point map oject.
MapRegion Class MapRegion stands for a map region object.
MapRoute Objects of this class store information about a single route in a directions result.
MapStep Objects of this class store information about a single step within a route in a directions result.
MapSymbol Map symbol used to display a point.
MapText Class MapText stands for a text map object.
